"यशु फेरि संसारको अन्तिम दिनमा धर्तीको परिक्षा गर्न फिर्ता आउनेछन।र तब सुकर्मीले अनन्त जीवन र दुष्कर्मीहरु हमेशा रुने छन्।

"The Holy Communion is the sacrament to commemorate the death of the Lord Jesus Christ. It enables us to partake of the flesh र blood of our Lord र to be in communion with Him so that we can have eternal life र be raised on the Last Day. This sacrament should be held as often as possible. Only one unleavened bread र grape juice is used".

